lead_paragraph: Rafa Nadal was worn out from his Rio Olympics exertions after emerging from an injury absence to win doubles gold, but the Spaniard perked back up with his trip to New York for the U.S. Open.

headline.print_headline: Energized Nadal Completes Straight-Sets Win in Opener
